#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.86"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.86:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.86:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga"
msgstr "9. Mindfulness"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 86. Yasasutta → nāgitasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.86:0.3"
msgid "86. Yasasutta"
msgstr "86. With Nāgita"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.341"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṃghena "
"saddhiṃ yena icchānaṅgalaṃ nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was wandering in the land of the Kosalans together "
"with a large Saṅgha of mendicants when he arrived at a village of the "
"Kosalan brahmins named Icchānaṅgala."

msgctxt "an8.86:1.2"
msgid "Tatra sudaṃ bhagavā icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe."
msgstr "He stayed in a forest near Icchānaṅgala."

msgctxt "an8.86:1.3"
msgid "Assosuṃ kho icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā:"
msgstr "The brahmins and householders of Icchānaṅgala heard:"

msgctxt "an8.86:1.4"
msgid ""
"“samaṇo khalu bho gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito icchānaṅgalaṃ "
"anuppatto icchānaṅgale viharati icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍe."
msgstr ""
"“It seems the ascetic Gotama—a Sakyan, gone forth from a Sakyan family—has "
"arrived at Icchānaṅgala. He is staying in a forest near Icchānaṅgala."

msgctxt "an8.86:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato:"
msgstr "He has this good reputation:"

msgctxt "an8.86:1.6"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho … pe …"
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’ …"

msgctxt "an8.86:1.7"
msgid "sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’”ti."
msgstr "It’s good to see such perfected ones.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā tassā rattiyā accayena pahutaṃ "
"khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ ādāya yena icchānaṅgalavanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bahidvārakoṭṭhake aṭṭhaṃsu uccāsaddā mahāsaddā."
msgstr ""
"Then, when the night had passed, they took many different foods and went to "
"the forest near Icchānaṅgala, where they stood outside the gates making a "
"dreadful racket."

msgctxt "an8.86:2.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nāgito bhagavato upaṭṭhāko hoti."
msgstr "Now, at that time Venerable Nāgita was the Buddha’s attendant."

msgctxt "an8.86:2.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ nāgitaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Nāgita:"

msgctxt "an8.86:2.4"
msgid "“ke pana te, nāgita, uccāsaddā mahāsaddā kevaṭṭā maññe macchavilope”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Nāgita, who’s making that dreadful racket? You’d think it was fishermen "
"hauling in a catch!”"

msgctxt "an8.86:2.5"
msgid ""
"“Ete, bhante, icchānaṅgalakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā pahutaṃ khādanīyaṃ "
"bhojanīyaṃ ādāya bahidvārakoṭṭhake ṭhitā bhagavantaṃyeva uddissa "
"bhikkhusaṃghañcā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, it’s these brahmins and householders of Icchānaṅgala. They’ve brought "
"many different foods, and they’re standing outside the gates wanting to "
"offer it specially to the Buddha and the mendicant Saṅgha.”"

msgctxt "an8.86:2.6"
msgid "“Māhaṃ, nāgita, yasena samāgamaṃ, mā ca mayā yaso."
msgstr "“Nāgita, may I never become famous. May fame not come to me."

#. VAR: nikāmalābhī → nikāmalābhī assaṃ (bahūsu)
msgctxt "an8.86:2.7"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, nāgita, nayimassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa "
"sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī assa akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. Yassāhaṃ "
"nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa "
"nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, "
msgstr ""
"There are those who can’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can. "

msgctxt "an8.86:2.8"
msgid "so taṃ mīḷhasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ lābhasakkārasilokasukhaṃ sādiyeyyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Let them enjoy the filthy, lazy pleasure of possessions, honor, and "
"popularity.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.342"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:3.1"
msgid "“Adhivāsetu dāni, bhante, bhagavā. Adhivāsetu sugato."
msgstr "“Sir, may the Blessed One please relent now! May the Holy One relent!"

msgctxt "an8.86:3.2"
msgid "Adhivāsanakālo dāni, bhante, bhagavato."
msgstr "Now is the time for the Buddha to relent."

msgctxt "an8.86:3.3"
msgid ""
"Yena yeneva dāni, bhante, bhagavā gamissati tanninnāva bhavissanti "
"brāhmaṇagahapatikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca."
msgstr ""
"Wherever the Buddha now goes, the brahmins and householders will incline the "
"same way, as will the people of town and country."

msgctxt "an8.86:3.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, thullaphusitake deve vassante yathāninnaṃ udakāni "
"pavattanti;"
msgstr "It’s like when it rains heavily and the water flows downhill."

msgctxt "an8.86:3.5"
msgid ""
"evamevaṃ kho, bhante, yena yeneva dāni bhagavā gamissati tanninnāva "
"bhavissanti brāhmaṇagahapatikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, wherever the Buddha now goes, the brahmins and householders "
"will incline the same way, as will the people of town and country."

msgctxt "an8.86:3.6"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an8.86:3.7"
msgid "Tathā hi, bhante, bhagavato sīlapaññāṇan”ti."
msgstr "Because of the Buddha’s ethics and wisdom.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:4.1"
msgid "“Māhaṃ, nāgita, yasena samāgamaṃ, mā ca mayā yaso."
msgstr "“Nāgita, may I never become famous. May fame not come to me."

msgctxt "an8.86:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, nāgita, nayimassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa "
"sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī assa akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. Yassāhaṃ "
"nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa "
"nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī, "
msgstr ""
"There are those who can’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can. "

msgctxt "an8.86:4.3"
msgid "so taṃ mīḷhasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ lābhasakkārasilokasukhaṃ sādiyeyya."
msgstr ""
"Let them enjoy the filthy, lazy pleasure of possessions, honor, and "
"popularity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.343"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: ekaccā nayimassa → ekaccā imassa (?)
#. VAR: assu → idaṃ padaṃ katthaci
#. VAR: akicchalābhiniyo → nikāmalābhiniyo akicchalābhiniyo (?)
msgctxt "an8.86:5.1"
msgid ""
"devatāpi kho, nāgita, ekaccā nayimassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa "
"upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhiniyo assu akicchalābhiniyo "
"akasiralābhiniyo, yassāhaṃ nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa "
"upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""
"Even some of the deities can’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can."

#. VAR: Tumhākampi → tāsampi (?)
#. VAR: anuyuttānaṃ viharataṃ → anuyutte viharante disvā (?)
msgctxt "an8.86:5.2"
msgid ""
"Tumhākampi kho, nāgita, saṅgamma samāgamma saṅgaṇikavihāraṃ anuyuttānaṃ "
"viharataṃ evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "When you all come together to enjoy each other’s company, I think:"

#. VAR: na hi nūname → naha nūna me (bj, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: assu → idaṃ padaṃ katthaci
msgctxt "an8.86:5.3"
msgid ""
"‘na hi nūname āyasmanto imassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa "
"upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhino assu akicchalābhino "
"akasiralābhino. Yassāhaṃ nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa "
"sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""
"‘These venerables mustn’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can."

msgctxt "an8.86:5.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi paname āyasmanto saṅgamma samāgamma saṅgaṇikavihāraṃ anuyuttā "
"viharanti’."
msgstr "That must be because they come together to enjoy each other’s company.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: aṅgulipatodakena → aṅgulipatodakehi (bj, pts1, mr) | aṅgulipaṭodakena (s1-3)
msgctxt "an8.86:6.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhū passāmi aññamaññaṃ aṅgulipatodakena sañjagghante "
"saṅkīḷante."
msgstr ""
"Take mendicants I see poking each other with their fingers, giggling and "
"playing together."

msgctxt "an8.86:6.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

msgctxt "an8.86:6.3"
msgid ""
"‘na hi nūname āyasmanto imassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa "
"upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhino assu akicchalābhino "
"akasiralābhino. Yassāhaṃ nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa "
"sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""
"‘These venerables mustn’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can."

msgctxt "an8.86:6.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi paname āyasmanto aññamaññaṃ aṅgulipatodakena sañjagghanti "
"saṅkīḷanti’. (1)"
msgstr ""
"That must be because they’re poking each other with their fingers, giggling "
"and playing together.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: panāhaṃ → idhāhaṃ (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an8.86:7.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhū passāmi yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā "
"seyyasukhaṃ passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyutte viharante."
msgstr ""
"Take mendicants I see eat as much as they like until their bellies are full, "
"then indulge in the pleasures of sleeping, lying, and drowsing."

msgctxt "an8.86:7.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

msgctxt "an8.86:7.3"
msgid ""
"‘na hi nūname āyasmanto imassa nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa "
"upasamasukhassa sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhino assu akicchalābhino "
"akasiralābhino. Yassāhaṃ nekkhammasukhassa pavivekasukhassa upasamasukhassa "
"sambodhasukhassa nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī."
msgstr ""
"‘These venerables mustn’t get the bliss of renunciation, the bliss of "
"seclusion, the bliss of peace, the bliss of awakening when they want, "
"without trouble or difficulty like I can."

msgctxt "an8.86:7.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi paname āyasmanto yāvadatthaṃ udarāvadehakaṃ bhuñjitvā seyyasukhaṃ "
"passasukhaṃ middhasukhaṃ anuyuttā viharanti’. (2)"
msgstr ""
"That must be because they eat as much as they like until their bellies are "
"full, then indulge in the pleasures of sleeping, lying, and drowsing.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.344"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
#. VAR: Idhāhaṃ → idha panāhaṃ (?)
msgctxt "an8.86:8.1"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi gāmantavihāriṃ samāhitaṃ nisinnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant living in the neighborhood of a village who I see sitting "
"immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "an8.86:8.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

#. VAR: imaṃ → idānimaṃ (katthaci)
#. VAR: upaṭṭhahissati → paccessati (bj) | saccessati (pts1) | upaṭṭhahati (mr)
#. VAR: Taṃ tamhā → so taṃ tamhā (?)
msgctxt "an8.86:8.3"
msgid ""
"‘idāni imaṃ āyasmantaṃ ārāmiko vā upaṭṭhahissati samaṇuddeso vā. Taṃ tamhā "
"samādhimhā cāvessatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Now a monastery worker, a novice, or a fellow practitioner will make this "
"venerable fall from immersion."

msgctxt "an8.86:8.4"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno na attamano homi gāmantavihārena. (3)"
msgstr ""
"So I’m not pleased that that mendicant is living in the neighborhood of a "
"village."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:9.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi āraññikaṃ araññe pacalāyamānaṃ "
"nisinnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant in the wilderness who I see sitting nodding in meditation."

msgctxt "an8.86:9.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

msgctxt "an8.86:9.3"
msgid ""
"‘idāni ayamāyasmā imaṃ niddākilamathaṃ paṭivinodetvā araññasaññaṃyeva manasi "
"karissati ekattan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Now this venerable, having dispelled that sleepiness and weariness, will "
"focus just on the unified perception of wilderness.’"

msgctxt "an8.86:9.4"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno attamano homi araññavihārena. (4)"
msgstr "So I’m pleased that that mendicant is living in the wilderness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:10.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi āraññikaṃ araññe asamāhitaṃ nisinnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant in the wilderness who I see sitting without being immersed "
"in samādhi."

msgctxt "an8.86:10.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

#. VAR: samādahissati → samādahessati (katthaci)
msgctxt "an8.86:10.3"
msgid ""
"‘idāni ayamāyasmā asamāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ samādahissati, samāhitaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"anurakkhissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Now if this venerable’s mind is not immersed in samādhi they will immerse "
"it; or if it is immersed in samādhi, they will preserve it.’"

msgctxt "an8.86:10.4"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno attamano homi araññavihārena. (5)"
msgstr "So I’m pleased that that mendicant is living in the wilderness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:11.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi āraññikaṃ araññe samāhitaṃ nisinnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant in the wilderness who I see sitting immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "an8.86:11.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, nāgita, evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "I think to myself:"

msgctxt "an8.86:11.3"
msgid ""
"‘idāni ayamāyasmā avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ vimuccissati, vimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ "
"anurakkhissatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Now this venerable will free the unfreed mind or preserve the freed mind.’"

msgctxt "an8.86:11.4"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno attamano homi araññavihārena. (6)"
msgstr "So I’m pleased that that mendicant is living in the wilderness."

#. </p><div class="var long-var" title="etthantare pāṭho 16A6:267 chakkanipāteyeva dissati, na ettha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:12.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi gāmantavihāriṃ lābhiṃ "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who I see living in the neighborhood of a village receiving "
"robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick."

msgctxt "an8.86:12.2"
msgid ""
"So taṃ lābhasakkārasilokaṃ nikāmayamāno riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, riñcati "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni;"
msgstr ""
"Enjoying possessions, honor, and popularity they neglect retreat, and they "
"neglect remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest."

msgctxt "an8.86:12.3"
msgid "gāmanigamarājadhāniṃ osaritvā vāsaṃ kappeti."
msgstr ""
"They come down to villages, towns and capital cities and make their homes "
"there."

msgctxt "an8.86:12.4"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno na attamano homi gāmantavihārena. (7)"
msgstr ""
"So I’m not pleased that that mendicant is living in the neighborhood of a "
"village."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an8.86:13.1"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, nāgita, bhikkhuṃ passāmi āraññikaṃ lābhiṃ "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take a mendicant who I see in the wilderness receiving robes, alms-food, "
"lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick."

msgctxt "an8.86:13.2"
msgid ""
"So taṃ lābhasakkārasilokaṃ paṭipaṇāmetvā na riñcati paṭisallānaṃ, na riñcati "
"araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni."
msgstr ""
"Fending off possessions, honor, and popularity they don’t neglect retreat, "
"and they don’t neglect remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest."

msgctxt "an8.86:13.3"
msgid "Tenāhaṃ, nāgita, tassa bhikkhuno attamano homi araññavihārena. (8)"
msgstr "So I’m pleased that that mendicant is living in the wilderness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
#. VAR: Yasmāhaṃ → yasmiṃhaṃ (katthaci)
msgctxt "an8.86:14.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmāhaṃ, nāgita, samaye addhānamaggappaṭipanno na kañci passāmi purato vā "
"pacchato vā, phāsu me, nāgita, tasmiṃ samaye hoti antamaso "
"uccārapassāvakammāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Nāgita, when I’m walking along a road and I don’t see anyone ahead or behind "
"I feel relaxed, even if I need to urinate or defecate.”"

#. </p></div><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.86:14.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
